'''Kanguka''' ni [[ikinyamakuru]] cyavutse mu 1988, cyandikaga inkuru zitandukanye, mu kwezi kwa 10/1990, cyahinduye umurongo cyijya gitangira kurwanya Leta yariho ya President [[Juvénal Habyarimana]], mu 1991, ubwo amashyaka menshi yemererwaga gukorera mu gihugu cyahise cyirwanya Leta k'umugaragaro. 

Kangura N° 80 ifite imirongo migari ikurikira: 
::Umupira w'Inkotanyi n'Abakombozi:Inkotanyi zirongeye ziradutsinze bahu!!!! Col SIMBA ati barambeshyera sindi umwicanyi kandi singa [[abatutsi]].

Twaraye mu Nkotanyi: 
::Wazinganya iki?Disikuru ya Ngango mu Nkotanyi.Twagiramungu yirukanwe mu ishyaka rya MDR none ari hafi gushinga MDR ye bwite.<ref>[http://www.genocidearchiverwanda.org.rw/index.php?title=Kanguka_Issue_80 www.genocidearchiverwanda.org.rw : Kanguka Issue 80]</ref> 
 
